				<div class="zw-contentpane selectableSection" style=" margin-top: 0px; position: relative;">
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">Dear Sir/ Madam  </p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">Thank you for choosing Pramati Care as your home care partner. This is to acknowledge that your enquiry has been received and will be processed soon.</p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">We at PramatiCare strive to provide the best Home Care experience to our customers.  </p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">Some of the salient features of our services are </p>
                        <ul style="list-style-type: disc">
                            <li><p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">Technical tie up with subject matter experts like Alzheimers society of India (ARDSI), St Stephan’s Hospital and Institute of Spinal injuries Center who provide technical and on the job training to our care givers</p></li>
                            <li><p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">Dedicated Relationship Manager as one point of contact for all queries and feedback  </p></li>
                            <li><p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">Robust quality control process, Mystery visits and regular client feedback to ensure quality of service delivery</p></li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">While we find the best suitable CG for you. Please find a crisp overview of our assignment process </p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);"><strong>Validation: </strong></p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">To understand you requirements better, our validation team will get in touch with you within an Hour.</p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);"><strong>Placement: </strong></p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">We use a highly refined matching algorithm to find the most suitable caregiver for your needs. The algorithm shortlists the CG based on multiple parameters (patient’s requirements, past work experience of the CG, ratings of CG). The trained caregiver will visit your place at the requested time. She/he will be accompanied by a QC (quality control) personnel who will help in ensuring the assigned CG performs the duty to your satisfaction.</p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);"><strong>Feedback: </strong></p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">We try our best to ensure that you have a pleasant experience & hence are always there to hear your concern and offer a solution. Since it is a manpower dependent service, we will appreciate your timely feedback in order to help us improve the quality of service.</p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);"><strong>Commercial Terms: </strong></p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">At the appointed hour, the Operations team will visit you to introduce the Caregiver and have the client contract signed. We will also be sending you a email invoice with 15 day advance payment which can be paid through online banking. Thereafter we will collect payment through online mode every 15 days.</p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">To keep a track of the service status, we have a customized Mobile Application. The app has multiple features which will surely make this association a fruitful experience. Using this app you can reach out to us at any time using the chat & call feature, you can mark the attendance of the CG, see the service details of your active services and much more. We will keep updating the App with new features to help you manage the service better. We would request you to please download the app at the earliest so that we can reach out to you using the mobile platform.</p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">For any query or feedback call us at 8010667766 </p>
                        <p class="zw-portion" data-text-len="15" style="color: rgb(111, 111, 111);">We are happy to serve you!!</p>

                        <p>Download our App from play store</p>
